==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overboil
<hw>O`ver*boil"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To boil over or
unduly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nor is discontent to keep the mind⟦br⟧
Deep in its fountain, lest it <qex>overboil</qex>⟦br⟧
In the hot throng.</q> <rj><qau>Byron.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overbold</ent>⟦br⟧
